N.I.N.A. Polaris
================

Browser-controlled astrophotography server. After installing this
package, open http://<hostname>.local:5000 from any device on your
LAN (laptop, tablet, phone) to access the full UI.

Key paths
---------

    /opt/polaris/                       Binary + assets
    /opt/polaris/appsettings.json       Editable config (conffile)
    /lib/systemd/system/polaris.service systemd unit
    /opt/polaris-indiweb-venv/          indi-web Python venv
    /home/polaris/files/                Captures (configurable in UI)
    /home/polaris/.config/NINA.Polaris/ Profiles, edits

Service control
---------------

    sudo systemctl status polaris
    sudo systemctl restart polaris
    sudo systemctl stop polaris
    journalctl -u polaris -f

Optional add-ons
----------------

ASTAP star catalog (recommended, ~290 MB):

    cd /tmp
    wget -O v50.deb https://downloads.sourceforge.net/project/astap-program/star_databases/v50_star_database.deb
    sudo dpkg -i v50.deb

GraXpert (AI post-processing). Not bundled because of license + ARM
binary unavailability. See online docs:

    https://github.com/DanWBR/NINA.Polaris/blob/master/docs/user-guide/raspberry-pi-setup.md#44-graxpert-manual-install

Documentation
